  <h2>See Me at RubyConf 2006</h2>
  <p class="auth">Posted by kev
  <span class="typo_date" title="Wed, 19 Jul 2006 16:13:00 GMT">Wed, 19 Jul 2006 16:13:00 GMT</span></p>
  <div id="adsense">
  <script type="text/javascript"><!--
